        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Welcome <a class="mention" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/u/wrxhokie">@Wrxhokie</a>. I believe what you need to do is store this template inside of an “Insert Text” action. If you do that, then the template tags take effect. Here’s the <a href="https://docs.getdrafts.com/docs/actions/steps/utility">documentation</a> for that.</p>
<p>You can also create a more complicated action which references this template draft to then create a new one every day (since this is for a daily note). If you need help putting that together, let me know.</p>
